OL,3,CPedestrian who died on A75 named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FA pedestrian who died on Sunday 3 May
OL,7,Fon the A75 has been named.
OL,9,FGraham Wight was killed in a crash on
OL,10,FSunday at around 3am after being
OL,11,Fstruck by a vehicle on the A75 between
OL,12,FLockerbie Road and the roundabout for
OL,13,Fthe A701.
OL,15,FEmergency services attended but the 43-
OL,16,Fyear-old was pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene.
