OL,3,CPedestrian who died on A75 named by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FRoad Policing Sergeant Wayne Carnochan
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,8,FGraham's family and friends at this
OL,9,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,11,F"Our enquiries into the crash continue
OL,12,Fand I'd like to thank everyone who has
OL,13,Fcome forward with information already.
OL,15,F"I'd ask anyone who hasn't yet spoken
OL,16,Fto police, and witnessed the collision
OL,17,For has dash-cam footage which could
OL,18,Fassist us, to get in touch."
